snippet.title: Baseball Advance (Game Boy Advance) - Gameplay
snippet.description: A full game of Baseball Advance, a 2002 baseball video game for the Nintendo GBA by Smilebit, Sega, and THQ. Vlad Guerrero and the Montreal Expos vs. Randy Johnson's Arizona Diamondbacks. A version of this game was released in Japan under the title Greatest Nine.
